1a:T41c,This is a surgical trial instrument set for the PCK knee replacement system. Internal evidence clearly indicates this is a complete set of stemmed femoral trials in multiple sizes (B, C, E, F, G, H) for both left and right anatomies. The 'PCK' designation indicates a specific knee system brand. Trial instruments are reusable surgical tools used during total knee arthroplasty to assess proper sizing and fit before final implant placement. Material is confirmed as surgical-grade stainless steel, appropriate for reusable instrumentation. However, review is required because: (1) The specific manufacturer 'PCK' brand ownership needs verification - PCK could be a Meril Life Sciences system or another manufacturer's system distributed by Meril; (2) No external sources available to confirm PCK system details; (3) Brand field is empty, creating ambiguity about system ownership. The product is correctly classified as an instrument set, but brand/system attribution requires human verification to ensure proper categorization and marketing accuracy.16:["$","$L19",null,{"product":{"product_name":"STEMMED FEMORAL TRIAL SET PCK","product_name_display":"STEMMED FEMORAL TRIAL SET PCK","sku_code":"MRL-CCL-001","product_family":"STEMMED FEMORAL TRIAL SET PCK","product_family_display":"Stemmed Femoral Trial Set Pck","slug":"stemmed-femoral-trial-set-pck","images":[{"id":"bce7624c6d5d","storage_path":"agile-ortho/products/69c17bd504841ec9248cfabb/cover_6899289c.jpg","original_filename":"cover_Destiknee Brochure.pdf.jpg","content_type":"image/jpeg","size":208705,"uploaded_at":"2026-03-26T05:55:44.917719+00:00","source":"division_fallback","width":1600,"height":1600}],"status":"published","live_visible":true,"brochure_url":"","seo_meta_title":"STEMMED FEMORAL TRIAL SET PCK | PCK Surgical Instruments - MedDevice Pro Telangana","seo_meta_description":"Complete set of stemmed femoral trials for PCK system in sizes B, C, E, F, G, H for both left and right.","pack_size":12,"size_variabl